OL,3,CNinth man arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cmurder of Merseyside teenager Ellis Cox
OL,6,FA ninth man's been arrested as part of
OL,7,Fthe investigation into the murder of a
OL,8,FLiverpool teenager as he cycled home.
OL,10,F19 year old Ellis Cox was shot dead at
OL,11,Fan industrial estate in Aintree nearly
OL,12,Ftwo years ago.
OL,14,FA 31-year-old man from Walton, has
OL,15,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fconspiracy to commit murder
OL,18,FAnother eight people remain under
OL,19,Finvestigation.
