OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781542112
OL,3,CNinth man arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cmurder of Merseyside teenager Ellis Cox
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Steve Wilkinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This month will mark two years
OL,8,Fsince Ellis was fatally shot at the
OL,9,FLiver Industrial Estate and his family
OL,10,Fhave been forced to live without
OL,11,Fanyone facing justice.
OL,13,F"We remain determined to find the
OL,14,Fpeople who were responsible and
OL,15,Falthough we have made this arrest it
OL,16,Fis vital that anyone who has
OL,17,Finformation comes forward as a matter
OL,18,Fof urgency so we can prosecute those
OL,19,Fwho were involved in Ellis's murder."
